<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yì rén de qí dǎo dà yǒu gōng xiào 迦南1234</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yì rén de qí dǎo dà yǒu gōng xiào, qiān wàn bù yào jí zào.
 shén yǒu tā de měi yì, yě yǒu tā de shí jiān biǎo.
 tā bì gěi nǐ kāi dào lù, bù chí yě bù zǎo.
 yī lù shàng tā bì gěi nǐ yù bèi, bù duō yě bù shǎo.
 jǔ qǐ shǒu suí shí dǎo gào, ràng zhǔ de míng dé róng yào.
 tā bì dìng fù xìng wǒ men de mín zú, ài huǒ zhèng zài chuán dì rán shāo.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1234</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>